title: Tiafoe, Taylor Swift & Travis Kelce celebrate Chiefs' win
description: Tennis, NFL football and pop music royalty enjoyed a rare three-way crossover on Sunday in Kansas City. The No. 18 in the PIF ATP Rankings Frances Tiafoe and his girlfriend Ayan Broomfield spent time with celebrity couple Travis Kelce and Taylor Swift after watching the Kansas City Chiefs overcome the Denver Broncos 16-14 in the AFC West. Music superstar Swift was at the game supporting her boyfriend Kelce, who plays as a tight end for the Chiefs. Although Tiafoe is a big Washington Commanders fan, that did not stop him and Broomfield from posting ‘Chiefsss’ on Instagram after their experience at Arrowhead Stadium. View this post on Instagram A post shared by ayan broomfield (@ayan.broomfield) [NEWSLETTER FORM]
